title: Rita Ora wore this crazy pink ensemble on The X Factor and Twitter couldn't cope
text:
Rita Ora wore this crazy pink ensemble on The X Factor and Twitter couldn't cope Rita Ora wore this crazy pink ensemble on The X Factor and Twitter couldn't cope 
Press Association 2014 / / National Entertainment News Share 
Rita Ora may have had a nail-biting decision to make over her acts on The X Factor, but it seems fans were more concerned about her choice of outfit. 
The 24-year-old singer went for a pink and black checked shirt, which we thought actually looked pretty cool. (ITV screenshot) 
Until of course, we saw that she paired it with a lace skirt in a print and texture clash horror. 
But the strangest thing of all was that her thigh-high boots matched her skirt. 
Twitter decided this was an epic wardrobe fail. Rita Ora is dressed like she's in the comfort tv advert! #XFactor pic.twitter.com/AKG7ar4MSm
